NAME
    PITA::XML - Create, load, save and manipulate PITA-XML files

STATUS
    This is an experimental release for demonstration purposes only.

    Please note the .xsd schema file may not install correctly as yet.

DESCRIPTION
    The "PITA::XML" package supports the various uses of XML throughout the
    PITA project.

SUPPORT
    Bugs should be reported via the CPAN bug tracker at

    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=PITA-XML>

    For other issues, contact the author.

AUTHOR
    Adam Kennedy <adamk@cpan.org>, <http://ali.as/>

